Seems like you GTX 980 ran out of memory. I'm not sure if that happened because it's not powerful enough, but you sure have plenty of VRAM on that thing.

Logs says it wanted to allocate 13GB of RAM, which seems wrong.

Are you launching a new campaign or an existing save? If the latter, your save may have a problem

I started a new campaign. after deleting the IntercepGame folder.
Yes, it looks like a memory leak. However the gtx980 with 8 GB of ram and my pc with 16 GB of Ram.
I never managed to get into the VAB...

I don't think I can help you

Maybe a dev will. Don't forget to send your issue withe the feedback feature.
